main_body:
Belgium is hereby authorized to grant aid totalling Bfrs 8 708 700 000 to the Belgian coal industry with effect from 1 January 1988 for the 1988 calendar year. The total amount shall be made up of the following aid:
1. Aid to cover operating losses not exceeeding Bfrs 6 151 600 000;
2. Aid to sales of coal and coke to the iron and steel industry of the Community not exceeding Bfrs 1 954 100 000;
3. Investment aid not exceeding Bfrs 600 000 000;
4. Aid to maintain a qualified work-force of underground staff not exceeding Bfrs 3 000 000.
